Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If cases were all men,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then I wonder if the unseen puzzles would be women?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chocolate is the fuse that wraps the case in the flames of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.48,0:24:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Airbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.45,0:24:32.91,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, those officers get their own love story!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.91,0:24:34.32,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ran, what do you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:36.54,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.90,0:03:26.78,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Mayuko Sakura (25)\NShop Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:41.27,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Yukihiko Tsujimoto (41)\NChocolatier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm charmed, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.38,0:24:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's called the Red Oily {\i1}Pssht{\i0} case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was it someone who has it in for the police...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey... haven't we seen that policewoman somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.19,0:24:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't she Officer Chiba's first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.65,0:24:18.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: Co-Investigating with a First Love (Part I)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:01.84,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:04.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.85,0:00:07.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We'll get to eat chocolates made by Yukihiko Tsujimoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:10.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,who won first place in the world championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.15,0:00:14.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And the shop's producer, Mayuko Sakura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is so young and beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:20.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So much that they say Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s success would've been impossible without her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the two of them are together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They make quite a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Made by a world-renowned chocolatier...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a beautiful shop producer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love Romance Chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you eat it together with someone you like, your love will come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Full-on girly talk, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.60,0:00:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I wanted to eat it with Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, eating something tasty with anyone will make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:52.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may say that, but didn't you want to eat it with Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:58.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We {\i1}are{\i0} going to eat it together though...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, it's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Le trésor de fruits. We've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a wonderful shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:21.86,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Suzuki Financial Group have given me their complete support,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,so everything here is first-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The store opens tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so you're our first customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we eat Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s chocolate in the shop too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The concept behind our shop is to allow you to eat freshly-made chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are those bottles liquor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a fruit liquor called nalewka,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,made by pickling fruit in strong liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! They all look lovely and tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do! So much so it makes you feel bad if you don't eat them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:04:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chocolates in this store are each shaped like jewels,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as the name of the store means the treasure of fruits in French.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are these fruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're pieces of the fruit in the fruit liquor on the rack made into chocolates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So would you like to try one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't drink liquor yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. The alcohol in it has been burnt away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then by all means I'll take a taste of adulthood...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your love may come true too, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then so will I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:41.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my {\i1}atelier{\i0}, Le trésor de fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the chocolatier, Yukihiko Tsujimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:47.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on winning first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an honour to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I too am honoured...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that such cute girls consider me so highly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a snob...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Ran Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is Sonoko Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:10.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a lady from the Suzuki Financial Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I expected, you have the elegance of nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must prepare, so please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy yourselves to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I should start preparing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that you can enjoy the first-place winning work that will be introduced at tomorrow's opening event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to announce your wedding tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting more and more jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady my ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's just a high school brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah well... if she's interested in me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it'll make it easier to get money from the Financial Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A photo to commemorate the end of bachelorhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s just so great after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? He's different from how I thought he'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s better than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Le trésor de fruits's opening ceremony hereby begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.84,0:06:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, the chocolatier who was honoured with the first place at the world championship,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukihiko Tsujimoto enters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the first Japanese showing of the chocolate titled {\i1}de l'espace{\i0}, to the stars...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:07:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ingredients are the top-class Criollo cacao and cocoa butter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a fruit liquor containing fruits carefully selected to bring out the fullest flavour of the chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost like a sculpture...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:12.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the main show has yet to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, beyond your dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me take you to a faraway galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So these are the flames of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:40.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i0}, call the fire brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yukihiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, have you found what started the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're still investigating, but it seems like the bottles that fell from this rack
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:28.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,contained a strongly alcoholic liquor, which caught fire and and caused it to spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the co-manager, Mayuko Sakura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would you say the fire started?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, the fruit liquor around the chocolate caught fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and surprised, Tsujimoto bumped into the rack and the bottles fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then, then Tsujimoto was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that inside was a fruit liquor called {\i1}nalewka{\i0}, made by placing fruit into {\i1}spirytus{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spirytus{\i0}? That's a vodka with 96% alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:09:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we've determined that Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s clothes were made from velvet pile, which burns very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who chose the fabric for his new cook's coat... I never thought this could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, let's go sit down over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that okay, Inspector Yuminaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, have you considered that the fire could've been caused by static electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The volatile alcohol in the fruit liquor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,gets ignited by static electricity in his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprised, Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} collided with the rack,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the liquor that spilled out of the bottles spread on the floor, and at once flames rose up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, since he was wearing fabric which burns easily,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.86,0:09:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the fire spread to Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, isn't it too early to decide that it was an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,caused by static electricity just because you can't find anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Brats shouldn't stick their noses in investigations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:06.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No... when the fruit liquor caught fire, a big flame rose up straight away...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:09.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A pistachio shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:11.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why would one be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:21.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could the pistachio shells have been left under the nalewka bottles to make them easier to topple over?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm only going to say this once, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A crime scene's not a playground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the fire spread, some flames got onto Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I quickly put it out myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why did Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s clothes get burnt too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing happened to any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to be clear, could you tell us exactly what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the fire spread,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and her friend tried to run, my sleeve suddenly caught fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it was probably a flying spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Sakura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were far away from Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, after handing the silver pot to Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, she was next to Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:17.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Certainly, after that, Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} never left Sonoko's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:25.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, come to think of it, after Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} poured the water into the chocolate's bowl, he had an odd expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:29.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As if something unexpected had happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, this thing was found near to the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The remains of burnt steel wool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:39.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? Steel wool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would that be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, there was a scrubbing brush made from steel wool in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, mister, what do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like non-woven fabric.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's used as an ingredient in packing materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's used a lot in deodorant bags, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kid, you sure know a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you think it's weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a deodorant be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were deodorants found in the fridge in the kitchen too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be odd for something from the kitchen to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, go back over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:26.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, he's wrong... If that was a deodorant bag, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:31.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There're some sort of crystals in the pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:38.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's it, salt, deodorant, steel wool, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:42.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}if I can just find the one missing piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! It seems like it was static that caused the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.09,0:12:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s scarf was made from nylon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.89,0:12:56.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When nylon is combined with a cotton fabric like velvet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it easily develops static electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So then it was just a static accident, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should go and have it looked at in hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine with something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, inspector! How long are you gonna keep injured people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the cause of the fire has been found, so it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:20.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no... At this rate they'll decide it was just an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:28.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my deduction is correct, it should still be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Ants are getting into the chocolate in the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? There aren't any ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's odd... I saw black things moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before the ants come back, shouldn't you collect and hold onto it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:58.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was right... This was no accident. It was a skillfully engineered murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, where did that brat with glasses get to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chocola-li-la-la...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've figured it out. The trick that murdered Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, girl, this was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An accidental fire caused by static electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}amai
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How naïve, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}amai
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sweeter than chocolate with lots of milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you tell me about this trick of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, I'll start explaining the fire by identifying its real source.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Among the evidence found at the crime scene, there are three key pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:15:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deodorant, salt crystals, and aluminium foil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:05.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Salt crystals and aluminium foil? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are salt crystals inside the silver pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aluminium foil was recently recovered by the officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the melted chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:20.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now I'll provide you with some entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, bring it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is what Sonoko-{\i1}néechan{\i0} asked me to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.49,0:15:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran-{\i1}néechan{\i0}, could you pour water from the teapot into each of the aluminium cups except the top one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That much is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.39,0:15:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a reproduction of the ignition method used in the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm? Beneath the origami crane, there's bright red steel wool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that what burned the crane?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is charcoal placed in the cup beneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:13.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the water in the pot is salt water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:17.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, you made an air battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using the phenomenon that electricity is created by a chemical reaction between aluminium and salt water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The materials of that air battery are the same as the items found at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That explains the fire's power, but how did the fire start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, when electricity flows through steel wool, it catches fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basically, the cause of the fire was not static, but an ignition switch comprised of those materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, what was that chocolate swan supposed to do when water was poured on it to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When doing so, Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me take you to a faraway galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably, dry ice was supposed to have been in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When water was poured on it, a white mist would flow out, creating the illusion of a galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer replaced the dry ice with an ignition switch made from an air battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not knowing that, Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} poured in the salt water himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,electrifying and igniting the steel wool, which set the fruit liquor on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hadn't knocked the bottles off the rack in surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then the fire wouldn't have risen up too much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those bottles had pistachio shells placed beneath them beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.25,0:17:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make them lean over and be easier to knock down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, pistachio shells had been found on the rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the killer's trap didn't end there. It was planned from even earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, think back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} {\i0}saw the fruit liquor had caught fire, was he that surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:18:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec, when the fruit liquor caught fire, Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} bumped into the rack...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:08.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right! Just before that, a huge flame rose up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. After that, the bottles fell and the fire grew larger,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I must have muddled up my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:20.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In such a dangerous place, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how was that huge flame she mentioned made?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beneath the table, the murderer set up a paper container full of {\i1}spirytus{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By doing so, the air beneath the tablecloth was filled with volatile alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So by pulling up the cloth just before the show, part of the alcohol was released.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was ignited by the burning fruit liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, just before the show started, you fixed up the tablecloth, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... Mayuko Sakura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be... Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, stop joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:10.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm suffering from being burnt too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that itself is what proves your guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason your sleeve caught fire is because when you set up the liquor beneath the table,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.60,0:19:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,part of the alcohol splashed onto your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why only her sleeve was burnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's just distorting events!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, will you tell me why you did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be... even the police suspect me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To begin with, that ignition switch is nothing more than things from the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's obvious you'd find them at the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It certainly is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you intentionally aimed to use such an intricate device.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This shop opens tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Contractors, administrators, many people have been in and out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:20:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't any of them have done it too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it cannot have been anyone but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, take my mobile out of my {\i1}pochette{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the photo I took earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The photo... this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just before the show started,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsujimoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} drank water from the pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it had been full of salt water, he would've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one who could've put salt in afterward... is {\i1}you{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was... nothing more than a tool to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost here... our dreams are finally coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, in setting up a shop in the best district in Tōkyō,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've come to be Japan's topmost chocolatier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's about time you should think about our wedding too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you've been deceived by the media too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You gave me various ideas to help me succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're my greatest tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tool...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:22.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But {\i1}my{\i0} dream came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have the greatest status and the greatest shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need any old tools anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll be fired at the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:40.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I loved and devoted myself to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he discarded me as if I had worn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.38,0:21:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayuko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I was going to lose everything anyway, then I wanted it to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him... this shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.22,0:22:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and my... love...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess if mysteries need the Great Deduction Queen Sonoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:45.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}toke
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then even I can solve a case once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:50.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}toke
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! The love crystal chocolate I wanted to eat with Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} melted!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.87,0:23:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... too much {\i1}toke{\i0} is a crime in itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:59.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And in the end, I didn't even get to eat a bite...
